Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
mustjoinallports_is_one_pin(25.10)          mustjoinallports_is_one_pin(25.10)

Name
       mustjoinallports_is_one_pin

Syntax
       mustjoinallports_is_one_pin {true | false}

       Type: Boolean

       Default: true

       If  false, the LEF MUSTJOINALLPORTS property on a LEF PIN automatically
       creates the MUSTJOIN pins for each PORT. If true, the MUSTJOIN pins are
       not created, but the router must be connected to every port with a sin-
       gle wire or single-via that physically overlaps all the ports.

